customer.preview.text: Dear Emnet\-Mesfin,  We hope this message finds you well. We have been attempting to reach out to you to discuss some concerns we've observed during your probationary period, but unfortunately, we haven't been able to connect, and our calls have gone unanswered.  Given the importance of this matter, we wanted to emphasize that if we don't hear back from you by February 26th, we will proceed with the assumption that you are choosing to terminate your contract with us.    However, if you are open to having a conversation, we genuinely want to hear your perspective and understand where any misunderstandings may lie. Your feedback is valuable to us, and we are committed to resolving any issues together. Please don't hesitate to reach out if you'd like to schedule a discussion.   We understand that there may have been challenges, particularly regarding training, and we appreciate your patience as we work to improve our processes moving forward. Our aim is always to support our team members to the best of our abili
